title: Secretar. Founded on the story of the Casket Letters
author: Beatty, W.
snippet: Dod, I thought I was the fule, but I see I'm wrang.

title: Secretar. Founded on the story of the Casket Letters
author: Beatty, W.
snippet: Dod, man, at the last ane on thehill, a gran' yin tae—hoo the limmers screicht and skirled—they used nae less than twenty leads o' peats, ae boll o' coal,forbye the tar barrels and the tow.

title: Secretar. Founded on the story of the Casket Letters
author: Beatty, W.
snippet: Dod !" said he to the others,"we maun rin for't, or the auld cleish ma claver'l stick to uslike a partan gif we bide ; it must have been the neist close,"and with that out they all ran helter-skelter.
